<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yǒng yuǎn gēn zhe yì xiàng 迦南226</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bǎi zhé bù huí bǎi liàn chéng gāng fēng yǔ zhōng áng qǐ tóu
 qiān xīn wàn kǔ qiān lǐ bīng fēng dà xuě yā bù fú
 wàn shuǐ qiān shān wàn lǐ zhēng tú zǒu guò nǐ de jiǎo bù
 lí kāi diē niáng yǐ jiān nán dāng bǐng yǒu yé sū jiù mǎn zú
 jīn cháo hēi yún mì bù míng cháo hǎi kuò tiān kōng
 dǔ xìn bù yí fàng dǎn wú jù yǒng yuǎn gēn zhe yì xiàng zǒu</lyrics>
<hymn_number>226</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>